= Battlefields =

'''Final Fantasy Mystic Quest''' uses numbered Battlefields for grinding EXP and GP.

__TOC__

== Overview ==

Battlefields are fixed encounter locations on the world map. Each Battlefield:
* Contains exactly 10 battles
* Can be repeated after completion
* Disappears from map when cleared (until reset)
* Resets when entering/exiting certain areas

