=== Efficiency Tips ===

* Use high battlefields for more EXP
* Match elemental weapons to enemy weaknesses
* White magic can clear groups quickly

== Rewards ==

=== Experience ===

Higher-numbered battlefields give more EXP:
* Early fields: Lower EXP per battle
* Late fields: Significant EXP gains

=== Gold (GP) ===

All enemies drop GP:
* Use for inns, item purchases
* Some fields more lucrative

=== Items ===

Some battlefield enemies drop:
* Cure potions
* Seeds
* Consumables

== Completion Bonus ==

When all 10 battles in a battlefield are won:
* Field temporarily disappears
* Bonus rewards possible
* Reset by entering/exiting regions

